      <a href="/journal/ux-as-an-independent-study" class="py-3 outline-2 outline-primary-70">UX as an Independent Study</a>
    </h3>
    <p>I’ve always been inclined to design my own educational experiences. I took independent study courses in school and
      designed my own major in college...</p>
